ONece up on a time there lived a MOnkey who resided on a jamun tree, which is located at the bank of river. 
In the same forest there lived a Crocodile and his wife....
One day the Crocodile came to the to the bank of river and rested under the tree.
The kind hearted monkey offerd him some fruits.
The Crocodile cameback the next day for some fruitsas he loed them .
As days passed by monkey and Crocodile became good friends.
